00:15:06.800 --> 00:15:08.080
 That's second turning.

00:15:08.080 --> 00:15:10.480
 Third turning is empty of other.

00:15:10.480 --> 00:15:12.840
 All the adventitious, temporary obscurations,

00:15:12.840 --> 00:15:16.160
 when they're removed, what's left?

00:15:16.160 --> 00:15:17.840
 The Buddha taught-- the tatagatagarbha,

00:15:17.840 --> 00:15:20.480
 the Buddha nature's left.

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:21.720
 This is the middleweight view.

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:26.360
 This is how our mind functions with all

