00:16:36.800 --> 00:16:42.320
 of Rongtong and Shintong, empty in self and empty of other.

00:16:42.320 --> 00:16:44.360
 Empty of any fixation at all.

00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:45.720
 That's called nondual wisdom.

00:16:45.720 --> 00:16:48.760
 And what is that like when it's empty of all the other things

00:16:48.760 --> 00:16:52.600
 that are unnatural and it's just entirely natural?

00:16:52.600 --> 00:16:54.920
 This is Buddha nature.

00:16:54.920 --> 00:16:57.800
 So this is the groundless ground.

00:16:57.800 --> 00:16:58.960
 This is the middleweight view.

