 Say, what is it like when you're abiding in emptiness?

00:46:28.520 --> 00:46:32.340
 All these amazing qualities come up.

00:46:32.340 --> 00:46:38.160
 The 10 powers and all the fearlessnesses and omnisciences

00:46:38.160 --> 00:46:41.540
 and all these clairs, the clairvoyances

00:46:41.540 --> 00:46:43.440
 and clairaudience and clairvisual

00:46:43.440 --> 00:46:45.760
 and all these things start happening

00:46:45.760 --> 00:46:48.840
 'cause now the alaya is being purified

