 And this is just said to be the natural state

00:46:56.560 --> 00:46:59.840
 of how mind is when it's not all gunked up

00:46:59.840 --> 00:47:01.120
 with habitual patterns.

00:47:01.120 --> 00:47:06.080
 That's why it's a definitive,

00:47:06.080 --> 00:47:08.740
 the definitive teaching is both Rangthong and shentong.

00:47:08.740 --> 00:47:11.200
 Conceptually, Prasangaka is the best one

00:47:11.200 --> 00:47:16.200
 to get us out of conceptual grasping, our hang ups,

00:47:16.200 --> 00:47:18.760
 holding on to this conceptual playground,

00:47:18.760 --> 00:47:21.420
 things that we like, our boxes, you know?

00:47:21.420 --> 00:47:25.240
 Prasangaka really shows that all these boxes are limited.

