 So, Middleweight View uses what's called transcendental logic

00:48:13.280 --> 00:48:18.280
 to reveal the ultimate open, flexible, empty nature

00:48:18.280 --> 00:48:21.880
 of every single relative experience.

00:48:21.880 --> 00:48:26.680
 It doesn't turn the dream off.

00:48:26.680 --> 00:48:28.080
 It wakes us up.

00:48:28.080 --> 00:48:31.080
 It makes us lucid so we can navigate the dream

00:48:31.080 --> 00:48:33.580
 to make it a better dream for all beings.

00:48:34.480 --> 00:48:38.920
 All dream-like beings make it a good dream for all of us.

00:48:38.920 --> 00:48:40.580
 The dream will never end.

00:48:40.580 --> 00:48:42.380
 We'll never not be in a box.

