 Oh, I like this way and that way,

00:51:34.920 --> 00:51:37.600
 and I have all these narratives and designations

00:51:37.600 --> 00:51:40.320
 and preferences and colors and fashions and fads and stuff.

00:51:40.320 --> 00:51:43.340
 They see how all those baby activities we're doing.

