 So sad, we've done it forever.

00:51:44.660 --> 00:51:45.760
 We're gonna keep doing it forever,

00:51:45.760 --> 00:51:46.960
 unless we stop doing it.

00:51:46.960 --> 00:51:49.840
 It's sad.

00:51:49.840 --> 00:51:52.080
 The Buddhists see that, so there's such compassion.

