 Then they give us all these stepping stones

00:51:54.680 --> 00:51:58.080
 to just finally just to set down the burden, you know?

00:51:58.080 --> 00:51:59.640
 Just like relax the mind.

00:51:59.640 --> 00:52:02.800
 Let it just be what it naturally is

00:52:02.800 --> 00:52:06.400
 with always kind of always in its own story, you know?

00:52:06.400 --> 00:52:11.560
 So we can see how typical, mundane, common sense,

00:52:11.560 --> 00:52:14.420
 contemporary discussions on almost everything

00:52:14.420 --> 00:52:18.440
 is a lot more superficial than this.

00:52:18.440 --> 00:52:20.320
 Buddhism's not throwing that out.

00:52:20.320 --> 00:52:23.240
 Buddhism meets all of us where we are.

