 Genuinely, the Buddha will genuinely experience

00:52:41.800 --> 00:52:43.960
 that with compassion, not with condemnation

00:52:43.960 --> 00:52:47.480
 or not kind of some I'm better than you approach.

00:52:47.480 --> 00:52:54.060
 The middle way view meets beings exactly where they are

00:52:54.060 --> 00:52:56.800
 in their dream and just helps it.

00:52:56.800 --> 00:52:58.380
 It's just a dream, you know?

