 You can wake up a little more.

00:53:00.440 --> 00:53:03.480
 And when we wake up, the dream doesn't stop.

00:53:03.480 --> 00:53:05.080
 We become lucid in the dream.

00:53:05.080 --> 00:53:08.800
 Then it's not a big problem anymore.

00:53:08.800 --> 00:53:11.280
 So that's the big fundamental insight

00:53:11.280 --> 00:53:15.440
 of the mind only, or sorry, the middle way view.

00:53:15.440 --> 00:53:18.440
 All of samsara's a false problem.

00:53:18.440 --> 00:53:21.440
 There's no samsara.

